Module com.gymbro
Package com.gymbro.utils

Class Transform

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gymbro.utils.Transform
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serialization
    public class Transform
extends java.lang.Object
implements Serialization
    Transform class containing one vector for position. One vector for scale and one double value for the amount of rotation. This is used on objects, so they can be placed in different places on the screen.
